{"tid":1486734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿港鐵未回應聯署　車長今日發起「靜坐不上車」抗議","createTime":"2019-08-19T03:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T05:13:29.000Z","uid":83131,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0d73b5d14dcb7f028b0c6c5509eba931e28c21","tid":1486734,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:21:01.000Z","msg":"早前有逾700港鐵車長及員工實名聯署，要求港鐵不要過度配合警方要求，並要求港鐵譴責對方各種影響鐵路安全的行動。有聯署發起人接受《立場》查詢，由於至今仍未得到港鐵管理層回覆，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲所有車長周一（19 日）自發「靜坐不上車」或「請假不上班」，抗議管理層未正視訴求，料大概有三成至四成當值車長參與</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n發起人指出，目前難以預料會否影響車務服務，由於港鐵已安排其他車長頂替，他估計需要六至七成當值車長參與才會影響服務。<br />\n<br />\n發起人提到，如選擇「靜坐不上車」的車長，會在每條綫的列車人員辦公室靜坐，不會有公開活動。葵青區區議員兼港鐵車長梁志成表示，得悉有車長明日發起抗議行動，他指出行動沒有大台，估計有 200 名車長參與，暫料不會影響車務。<br />\n<br />\n參與實名聯署的700名港鐵員工，逾九成為車長，來自東鐵綫、西鐵綫、港島綫、觀塘綫、高鐵綫等，有約20人是「列車員工督察」。實名聯署的車長早前譴責港鐵草菅人命，要求港鐵管理層促請警方展開行動前先考慮港鐵員工及乘客安全，避免使用大規模武力如橡膠子彈、催淚彈等<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大佬!? 邊個知呀!? 我今日返工咁順暢既? 仲睇緊尋日遊行既新聞 喂!?咁就叫升左級!? po上黎比大家同你宣傳下嘛!!!</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7-%E9%9D%9C%E5%9D%90%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A-%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E9%259D%259C%25E5%259D%2590%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=fc62b394\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E9%259D%259C%25E5%259D%2590%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&h=9ea29b18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7-%E9%9D%9C%E5%9D%90%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A-%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"ba56838c7b22712c61845b4fdc47bbfcec93c41f","tid":1486734,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"兩次都好似搞唔成<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自由之書&mdash;賣卡投資國難五金發國難財Ver 2.0</span></span><br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"0c5a9b6e81838b9566a25759b05903b38d2cecb2","tid":1486734,"uid":83131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"星期日凌晨叫人行動,邊個睇到呀..."},{"pid":"79cdad69e63ed5bc07f8765c4a01187d3c4d93c7","tid":1486734,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"多謝港鐵車長<br />\n希望你地繼續抗爭<br />\n直至管理層回覆為止"},{"pid":"aa2669089480f1cee0c79eef7d33b4a2f4d8b3ac","tid":1486734,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"希望有更多車長一齊參與 !!"},{"pid":"74b0faf213727e6acdfa467496858f906370b4ec","tid":1486734,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ded41dca1aee9e575722981685830040a91c3a","tid":1486734,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"好似唔覺有新聞     搞唔成？"}]}